                <supplied reason="lost">Marti Ultori</supplied> <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>erator</ex></expan> Caesar divi</supplied> <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">Nervae <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> Nerva</supplied> <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">Traianus <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Germ</abbr><ex>anicus</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">Dacicus <expan><abbr>trib</abbr><ex>unicia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pot</abbr><ex>estate</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="6"/><supplied reason="lost">XIII po</supplied><expan><abbr>nt</abbr><ex>ifex</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>max</abbr><ex>imus</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="7"/><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>imp</abbr><ex>erator</ex></expan> VI</supplied> <expan><abbr>co</abbr><ex>n</ex></expan><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ul</ex></expan> V <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ater</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>atriae</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="8"/><supplied reason="lost">exer</supplied>citu D<supplied reason="lost">ecebali</supplied> <lb n="9"/><supplied reason="lost">Daco</supplied>rum <supplied reason="lost">regis su</supplied><lb break="no" n="10"/>[perato ------
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Gefunden im Südturm des Osttors. Ergänzungsvorschlag nach Ciurea und Gostar. Nach Doruţiu-Boilă, Gostar, Ciurea und Florescu eine von zwei identischen Inschriften am Tropaeum Traiani (vgl. AE 1972, 521b = AE 1996, 1355a = CIL III 12467); nach Alexandrescu Vianu nicht zum Tropaeum Traiani gehörig. (B): Doruţiu-Boilă; AE 1965: Leseabweichungen.</p>
            </div>
